Decision justification:
- I choose Physical Graffiti because its features align with my core priorities: a cohesive, album‑length listening experience with rootsy, bluesy guitar work, layered textures, dynamic and organic mastering, and sequencing that rewards attentive playthrough on CD. Those attributes fit my preference for records that present a unified sonic and narrative identity and make full use of the CD format’s midrange and dynamics.
