  - It emphasizes vintage acoustic textures and a rootsy, live feel — great for organic ensemble fans, but less aligned with my preference for pronounced keyboard/synth accents and the larger-scale, multi‑tracked studio layering that creates the memorable AOR/Greatest‑Hits sheen I favor.
